Coding Style
============

  KNotes conforms to the KDEPIM Coding Standard:

    http://kdepim.kde.org/development/coding.php


Rules
=====

  You are free to hack away :-)

  But *please* remember to:

    * Update the ChangeLog
    * Update the AUTHORS
    * Update the TODO

  Any major changes must be approved and might require 
you to branch off and merge when finished. :-)


Need Help
=========

